<A>__{three men, standing close together in the path. beyond them can be seen the waters of florin channel. the three men are not your everyday commuter types. standing in front is a tiny man with the most angelic face. he is sicilian and his name is vizzini. beside him is a spaniard, erect and taut as a blade of steel. his name is inigo montoya. beside him is a giant. his name is fezzik.}
